      "message": "Two reasons:\n* We don\u0027t cache non-closed builds because they may still mutate\n* If a request is sent for a build after buildbucket knows about the build but before the pubsub pipeline has finished (e.g. this is possible if luci-notify receives a build event before milo), we still want milo to be able to respond correctly\n\nAdded comment to clarify.",
